1
00:00:17,000 --> 00:00:20,000
- [atmospheric music playing]
- [insects trilling]

2
00:00:47,250 --> 00:00:50,416
[man] The Blue Angel Creed!

3
00:00:50,500 --> 00:00:52,208
[group] As a Blue Angel,

4
00:00:52,291 --> 00:00:57,208
I will dedicate all my efforts to pride,
professionalism and perfection.

5
00:00:57,291 --> 00:01:02,083
<i>I will strive to honor the crest I earned
and the flag I wear,</i>

6
00:01:02,166 --> 00:01:05,458
<i>but I will never forget from where I came.</i>

7
00:01:05,541 --> 00:01:08,708
<i>Once a Blue Angel, always a Blue Angel.</i>

